{"tid":2228512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角騷亂示威者過堂 記者想扯示威者口罩影樣 《蘋果》攝記：做得出就唔好怕人影啦","createTime":"2020-10-03T15:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T03:04:57.000Z","uid":30719,"like":8,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ced7eeb6eb84531c83da4e82878b71e832bb8915","tid":2228512,"uid":30719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2016/02/apple-daily-camera-man-get-in-trouble/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F02%2Fapple-daily-camera-man-get-in-trouble%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=eb5b00b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2016/02/apple-daily-camera-man-get-in-trouble/</a></blockquote><br />\n大年初一旺角騷動被捕的三十八名市民，今日在九龍城裁判法院應訊，他們離開法庭時，在場記者一湧而上，有記者想扯低示威者口罩影樣。一名《蘋果日報》攝影記者上前拍攝被捕市民的容貌，企圖扯下他們的口罩，並說：「做得出就唔好怕人影啦。」現場市民起哄，並與該攝影師口角，情況一度混亂，《蘋果日報》在下午四時出新聞，表示該報與攝記馬泉崇就有關言行，向在場人士致歉。<br />\n<br />\n但不少網民並不收貨。網民Edward Tang批評記者行業長期濫用「新聞自由」的光環，囂張跋扈已久，個別事件背後是非一日之寒的長期現象：「家陣的傳媒，大把呢類蛇蟲鼠蟻；『新聞自由』四個大家就縱容包庇害群之馬。睇到《蘋果》個聲明，私私縮縮，發生咩事唔敢講唔敢報返出嚟，輕輕帶過，咁叫做負責任嘅傳媒？垃圾都不如。」<br />\n<br />\n在《蘋果》的道歉新聞下，網民zkwai123說：「將心比心啦你，人地都戴左口罩，咁咩事要俾你拉開個口罩影丫，姐係你有日死左，記者要打開你流曬血既屍體要影你一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n社運人士鄭錦滿表示，在現場的混亂中被記者搶走眼鏡，他說：「我唔肯定係咪蘋果 記者，如果你地知邊位行家拾獲，請聯絡我交還﹗」<br />\n<br />\n今日有三十八人提堂，當中一人被改控非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2016/02/apple-daily-camera-man-get-in-trouble\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F02%2Fapple-daily-camera-man-get-in-trouble&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=fc189bc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2016/02/apple-daily-camera-man-get-in-trouble</a><br />\n<br />\n大家做乜都好，記住蘋果同本土派係對立的。下面想留熱狗，分化撚，回帶撚既收收皮先。"},{"pid":"70cb6b4872dd270876ca1593dbfd132a8ae27ee5","tid":2228512,"uid":377096,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:41:01.000Z","msg":"16年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba6265d67ef8d37d429358778edc9bf7c3df047","tid":2228512,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83e1dc58290d77ca48b28dc1f83c2d38174515c6","tid":2228512,"uid":142954,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"蘋果會咁做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c469ad4b699ed2361de46113c1108b29a3f5108","tid":2228512,"uid":7699,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"蘋果立場不嬲都係反本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係班細蚊仔唔知當蘋果神咁拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84d7fb3a8b6e8d963dcfe3edceacb9281388b03","tid":2228512,"uid":269712,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"Copy 舊文, 打幾隻字想收人三毛, 俾多少少心機 好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">不推文回覆 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ce7f8feff869a2aa25326713e7c3ea4e4d943ffc","tid":2228512,"uid":285514,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"83e1dc58290d77ca48b28dc1f83c2d38174515c6","tid":2228512,"uid":142954,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"蘋果會咁做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"16年抹黑天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0edce095c5d09a054c514278b05b4ced40aa022","tid":2228512,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"馬泉崇仲繼續有出現"},{"pid":"d215df49bb9e3716c6bfee4116e01e82645b6c8e","tid":2228512,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83e1dc58290d77ca48b28dc1f83c2d38174515c6","tid"